{"ps1.10:0.1":"Patisambhidamagga ","ps1.10:0.2":"1 Mahavagga ","ps1.10:0.3":"1.10. Mandapeyyakatha ","ps1.10:1.1":"“Mandapeyyamidam, bhikkhave, brahmacariyam. ","ps1.10:1.2":"Sattha sammukhibhuto tidhattamando. ","ps1.10:1.3":"Satthari sammukhibhute desanamando, patiggahamando, brahmacariyamando”. ","ps1.10:2.1":"Katamo <b>desanamando?</b> ","ps1.10:2.2":"Catunnam ariyasaccanam acikkhana desana pannapana patthapana vivarana vibhajana uttanikammam, catunnam satipatthananam …pe… ","ps1.10:2.3":"catunnam sammappadhananam … ","ps1.10:2.4":"catunnam iddhipadanam … ","ps1.10:2.5":"pancannam indriyanam … ","ps1.10:2.6":"pancannam balanam … ","ps1.10:2.7":"sattannam bojjhanganam … ","ps1.10:2.8":"ariyassa atthangikassa maggassa acikkhana desana pannapana patthapana vivarana vibhajana uttanikammam—","ps1.10:2.9":"ayam desanamando. ","ps1.10:3.1":"Katamo <b>patiggahamando?</b> ","ps1.10:3.2":"Bhikkhu bhikkhuniyo upasaka upasikayo deva manussa ye va panannepi keci vinnataro—","ps1.10:3.3":"ayam patiggahamando. ","ps1.10:4.1":"Katamo <b>brahmacariyamando?</b> ","ps1.10:4.2":"Ayameva ariyo atthangiko maggo, seyyathidam—","ps1.10:4.3":"sammaditthi, sammasankappo, sammavaca, sammakammanto, sammaajivo, sammavayamo, sammasati, sammasamadhi—","ps1.10:4.4":"ayam brahmacariyamando. ","ps1.10:5.1":"Adhimokkhamando saddhindriyam, assaddhiyam kasato; ","ps1.10:5.2":"assaddhiyam kasatam chaddetva saddhindriyassa adhimokkhamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:5.3":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:5.4":"Paggahamando viriyindriyam, kosajjam kasato; ","ps1.10:5.5":"kosajjam kasatam chaddetva viriyindriyassa paggahamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:5.6":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:5.7":"Upatthanamando satindriyam, pamado kasato; ","ps1.10:5.8":"pamadam kasatam chaddetva satindriyassa upatthanamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:5.9":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:5.10":"Avikkhepamando samadhindriyam, uddhaccam kasato; ","ps1.10:5.11":"uddhaccam kasatam chaddetva samadhindriyassa avikkhepamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:5.12":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:5.13":"Dassanamando pannindriyam, avijja kasato; ","ps1.10:5.14":"avijjam kasatam chaddetva pannindriyassa dassanamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:5.15":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:6.1":"Assaddhiye akampiyamando saddhabalam, assaddhiyam kasato; ","ps1.10:6.2":"assaddhiyam kasatam chaddetva saddhabalassa assaddhiye akampiyamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:6.3":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:6.4":"Kosajje akampiyamando viriyabalam, kosajjam kasato; ","ps1.10:6.5":"kosajjam kasatam chaddetva viriyabalassa kosajje akampiyamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:6.6":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:6.7":"Pamade akampiyamando satibalam, pamado kasato; ","ps1.10:6.8":"pamadam kasatam chaddetva satibalassa pamade akampiyamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:6.9":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:6.10":"Uddhacce akampiyamando samadhibalam, uddhaccam kasato; ","ps1.10:6.11":"uddhaccam kasatam chaddetva samadhibalassa uddhacce akampiyamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:6.12":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:6.13":"Avijjaya akampiyamando pannabalam, avijja kasato; ","ps1.10:6.14":"avijjam kasatam chaddetva pannabalassa avijjaya akampiyamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:6.15":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:7.1":"Upatthanamando satisambojjhanga, pamado kasato; ","ps1.10:7.2":"pamadam kasatam chaddetva satisambojjhangassa upatthanamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:7.3":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:7.4":"Pavicayamando dhammavicayasambojjhango, avijja kasato; ","ps1.10:7.5":"avijjam kasatam chaddetva dhammavicayasambojjhangassa pavicayamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:7.6":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:7.7":"Paggahamando viriyasambojjhango, kosajjam kasato; ","ps1.10:7.8":"kosajjam kasatam chaddetva viriyasambojjhangassa paggahamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:7.9":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:7.10":"Pharanamando pitisambojjhango, parilaho kasato; ","ps1.10:7.11":"parilaham kasatam chaddetva pitisambojjhangassa pharanamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:7.12":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:7.13":"Upasamamando passaddhisambojjhango, dutthullam kasato; ","ps1.10:7.14":"dutthullam kasatam chaddetva passaddhisambojjhangassa upasamamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:7.15":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:7.16":"Avikkhepamando samadhisambojjhango, uddhaccam kasato; ","ps1.10:7.17":"uddhaccam kasatam chaddetva samadhisambojjhangassa avikkhepamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:7.18":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:7.19":"Patisankhanamando upekkhasambojjhango, appatisankha kasato; ","ps1.10:7.20":"appatisankham kasatam chaddetva upekkhasambojjhangassa patisankhanamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:7.21":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:8.1":"Dassanamando sammaditthi, micchaditthi kasato; ","ps1.10:8.2":"micchaditthim kasatam chaddetva sammaditthiya dassanamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:8.3":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:8.4":"Abhiniropanamando sammasankappo, micchasankappo kasato; ","ps1.10:8.5":"micchasankappam kasatam chaddetva sammasankappassa abhiniropanamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:8.6":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:8.7":"Pariggahamando sammavaca, micchavaca kasato; ","ps1.10:8.8":"micchavacam kasatam chaddetva sammavacaya pariggahamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:8.9":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:8.10":"Samutthanamando sammakammanto, micchakammanto kasato; ","ps1.10:8.11":"micchakammantam kasatam chaddetva sammakammantassa samutthanamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:8.12":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:8.13":"Vodanamando sammaajivo, micchaajivo kasato; ","ps1.10:8.14":"micchaajivam kasatam chaddetva sammaajivassa vodanamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:8.15":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:8.16":"Paggahamando sammavayamo, micchavayamo kasato; ","ps1.10:8.17":"micchavayamam kasatam chaddetva sammavayamassa paggahamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:8.18":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:8.19":"Upatthanamando sammasati, micchasati kasato; ","ps1.10:8.20":"micchasatim kasatam chaddetva sammasatiya upatthanamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:8.21":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:8.22":"Avikkhepamando sammasamadhi, micchasamadhi kasato; ","ps1.10:8.23":"micchasamadhim kasatam chaddetva sammasamadhissa avikkhepamandam pivatiti—","ps1.10:8.24":"mandapeyyam. ","ps1.10:9.1":"Atthi mando, atthi peyyam, atthi kasato. ","ps1.10:9.2":"Adhimokkhamando saddhindriyam, assaddhiyam kasato; ","ps1.10:9.3":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:9.4":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:9.5":"Paggahamando viriyindriyam, kosajjam kasato; ","ps1.10:9.6":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:9.7":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:9.8":"Upatthanamando satindriyam, pamado kasato; ","ps1.10:9.9":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:9.10":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:9.11":"Avikkhepamando samadhindriyam, uddhaccam kasato; ","ps1.10:9.12":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:9.13":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:9.14":"Dassanamando pannindriyam, avijja kasato; ","ps1.10:9.15":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:9.16":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:10.1":"Assaddhiye akampiyamando saddhabalam, assaddhiyam kasato; ","ps1.10:10.2":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:10.3":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:10.4":"Kosajje akampiyamando viriyabalam, kosajjam kasato; ","ps1.10:10.5":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:10.6":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:10.7":"Pamade akampiyamando satibalam, pamado kasato; ","ps1.10:10.8":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:10.9":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:10.10":"Uddhacce akampiyamando samadhibalam, uddhaccam kasato; ","ps1.10:10.11":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:10.12":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:10.13":"Avijjaya akampiyamando pannabalam, avijja kasato; ","ps1.10:10.14":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:10.15":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:11.1":"Upatthanamando satisambojjhango, pamado kasato; ","ps1.10:11.2":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:11.3":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:11.4":"Pavicayamando dhammavicayasambojjhango, avijja kasato; ","ps1.10:11.5":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:11.6":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:11.7":"Paggahamando viriyasambojjhango, kosajjam kasato; ","ps1.10:11.8":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:11.9":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:11.10":"Pharanamando pitisambojjhango, parilaho kasato; ","ps1.10:11.11":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:11.12":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:11.13":"Upasamamando passaddhisambojjhango, dutthullam kasato; ","ps1.10:11.14":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:11.15":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:11.16":"Avikkhepamando samadhisambojjhango, uddhaccam kasato; ","ps1.10:11.17":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:11.18":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:11.19":"Patisankhanamando upekkhasambojjhango, apatisankha kasato; ","ps1.10:11.20":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:11.21":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:12.1":"Dassanamando sammaditthi, micchaditthi kasato; ","ps1.10:12.2":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:12.3":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:12.4":"Abhiniropanamando sammasankappo, micchasankappo kasato; ","ps1.10:12.5":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:12.6":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:12.7":"Pariggahamando sammavaca, micchavaca kasato; ","ps1.10:12.8":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:12.9":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:12.10":"Samutthanamando sammakammanto, micchakammanto kasato; ","ps1.10:12.11":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:12.12":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:12.13":"Vodanamando sammaajivo, micchaajivo kasato; ","ps1.10:12.14":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:12.15":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:12.16":"Paggahamando sammavayamo, micchavayamo kasato; ","ps1.10:12.17":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:12.18":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:12.19":"Upatthanamando sammasati, micchasati kasato; ","ps1.10:12.20":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:12.21":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:12.22":"Avikkhepamando sammasamadhi, micchasamadhi kasato; ","ps1.10:12.23":"yo tattha attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso—","ps1.10:12.24":"idam peyyam. ","ps1.10:13.1":"Dassanamando sammaditthi … ","ps1.10:13.2":"abhiniropanamando sammasankappo … ","ps1.10:13.3":"pariggahamando sammavaca … ","ps1.10:13.4":"samutthanamando sammakammanto … ","ps1.10:13.5":"vodanamando sammaajivo … ","ps1.10:13.6":"paggahamando sammavayamo … ","ps1.10:13.7":"upatthanamando sammasati … ","ps1.10:13.8":"avikkhepamando sammasamadhi. ","ps1.10:14.1":"Upatthanamando satisambojjhango … ","ps1.10:14.2":"pavicayamando dhammavicayasambojjhango … ","ps1.10:14.3":"paggahamando viriyasambojjhango … ","ps1.10:14.4":"pharanamando pitisambojjhango … ","ps1.10:14.5":"upasamamando passaddhisambojjhango … ","ps1.10:14.6":"avikkhepamando samadhisambojjhango … ","ps1.10:14.7":"patisankhanamando upekkhasambojjhango. ","ps1.10:15.1":"Assaddhiye akampiyamando saddhabalam … ","ps1.10:15.2":"kosajje akampiyamando viriyabalam … ","ps1.10:15.3":"pamade akampiyamando satibalam … ","ps1.10:15.4":"uddhacce akampiyamando samadhibalam … ","ps1.10:15.5":"avijjaya akampiyamando pannabalam. ","ps1.10:16.1":"Adhimokkhamando saddhindriyam … ","ps1.10:16.2":"paggahamando viriyindriyam … ","ps1.10:16.3":"upatthanamando satindriyam … ","ps1.10:16.4":"avikkhepamando samadhindriyam … ","ps1.10:16.5":"dassanamando pannindriyam. ","ps1.10:17.1":"Adhipateyyatthena indriya mando, akampiyatthena bala mando, niyyanatthena bojjhanga mando, hetutthena maggo mando, upatthanatthena satipatthana mando, padahanatthena sammappadhana mando, ijjhanatthena iddhipada mando, tathatthena sacca mando, avikkhepatthena samatho mando, anupassanatthena vipassana mando, ekarasatthena samathavipassana mando, anativattanatthena yuganaddha mando, samvaratthena silavisuddhi mando, avikkhepatthena cittavisuddhi mando, dassanatthena ditthivisuddhi mando, muttatthena vimokkho mando, pativedhatthena vijja mando, pariccagatthena vimutti mando, samucchedatthena khaye nanam mando, patippassaddhatthena anuppade nanam mando, chando mulatthena mando, manasikaro samutthanatthena mando, phasso samodhanatthena mando, vedana samosaranatthena mando, samadhi pamukhatthena mando, sati adhipateyyatthena mando, panna taduttaratthena mando, vimutti saratthena mando, amatogadham nibbanam pariyosanatthena mandoti. ","ps1.10:17.2":"Mandapeyyakatha nitthita. ","ps1.10:17.3":"Catutthabhanavaro. ","ps1.10:17.4":"Mahavaggo pathamo. ","ps1.10:17.5":"Tassuddanam ","ps1.10:18.1":"Nanaditthi ca assasa, ","ps1.10:18.2":"indriyam vimokkhapancama; ","ps1.10:18.3":"Gatikammavipallasa, ","ps1.10:18.4":"maggo mandena te dasati. ","ps1.10:18.5":"Esa nikayadharehi thapito, asamo pathamo pavaro varavaggoti. "}